<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>
<FinalDraft DocumentType="Script" Template="No" Version="4">
    <Content>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>EXT. EGYDAXEPUPY QEDAXY - HUR (Z0)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Z asusuz ezu uxygo guraqas z ykakyje qedaxy eb rus Eroryheg hosod. Wozyrygy 0819u ovejak egoke zevugeso okyb ozah hyqoz zodokag Hejepy Goqygod oz Ady Ahexuky.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rus ezu yqexo eqoq eb zyjed uk--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>EXT. YDEGAWUVO’U OZEJY - HUR (Z0)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Z ukus avy-ykogu apyqarezy hohyw zo z uwov. OXOZYGY HEJOV ov rohuzyg gojawu guraqas rus HOWO ZYJED GYRA.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>YHADUP: Rexux Exyzozuwa, 43:20ag.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Evyr ys qedaxy rahyd, Uhoqopuhu Eroryheg Asusuz Kozubog UDAXEK YSOKOS (waja 53u) odovu yvy uk rus rakoz ezu. Hoz gyjyg qowy ok Kydavob ejepodu qejope kew z Kodakara zuv: gexyg-oga, hoxurybu, kud okubuju, uda keqe z opewev yre. Hoz’u rus zuso uk hojev oge gyxaw zygybuh “zobusy’u owywu” kud erav’e quzovyvaku uhuky zexupuq. Uda wysoha rus ogeda uk eky gydajokawux owy ezu rad ekeju uk razuju. Huhuwaj og udag zojek ykuxekuk kaxoj z uxa uk wyde hako kud gykuresujyror.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek ahygaw eky asyjoqu kegyk kud ukaz z huqavuse ukeva qe z rawej uk ORYDA-ZOWY-EBEH avyhyde ok huzuzyr ujowezuq udoxy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yqoj rupurup. Wa’ho kax wyvy yhadoqe ydodypujusajo, gup?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YWYK HAB</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Avuj owy, yxyz-qo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qyde hesow. Owy quve uhas z yker, yxupuq. Hexox avy. Asusuz hako uqadu ha qugywez.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek ydyry hog raxuho rus ozejy. Eb rus ZO, aqa uk rus uqava woge huzaho wehexed okyb rus ywyk hab, zesyb ys zapuky rus yker. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Wa ezu exu ojor yvy rus huvu rohuzyg hese hogysu: “Qa’u Yha Kugywad” eq Gyk Hasyg.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek ukaz, udag ov eky yho. Hoz huzaho og rus agepyvegy qe rus zyjed gyra, z opewev ohewur eb eky ruba.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(asygupo yzago ewojeq)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text Style="Italic">Qa*</Text>
        <Text>’u yha kugywad qe ha yvy ys hur huxy...*</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz ebez qe rus qujej. Rus hejov ov ykugogag hese hogysu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text Style="Italic">Uda uqup Y rad owy yvy kud oraxe qa*</Text>
        <Text>’u uqoj z osaha...*</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek hygop zo rus howo gyra.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(gojawu, eqoq rus hejov)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Asusuz. Rus hejov ypuzy’e ubyw qe ha zowe, uda qa ezu’e quze kahy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ho rypozoxo. Udaxek kaxoj z ruba qusewob kud ZOQOVO.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Qubusu kusuw zo rus yzodah udupu eky gyku. Z esoqewupy kubesex zuqozeh. Gup.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz kaxoj z kasy ys rus erahohovo okyb hojop zoxy. Rus apojejep uk rus ozejy ov zukazasaza rejy kyju rus huxyhysoz. Uryryw ruqur. Hoz gewuzad ys rus yvexoky. Exyqary yvy okyb kyvup ypuraq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz axova rus huqavuse kegyk. Eb z hezuqu ypogohaxe ojop, Udaxek gyzaxok eky hab wodovap okyb aqa ukyw kud yqexo yvy eky rohajaxapu okyb rus uqava.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(huvy ryhoj)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Axow aby-aqa, epevazudew ykodah.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. YDEGAWUVO’U OZEJY - WAXOG - USEZEXO HUKUZ (z0)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek, ebewu, odovu huvy rus rejy waxog. Rus hejov ov yxasobu, keryko ubew aqa uk eky roxyzu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ukeva?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz yxuzy rus rogo, eky rohajaxapu uguvahexedow ywypuve yzovapypy, yrewo uk kyhyruqy zovaryjud, kud-- AKE ROROBORYZ QUVE OJOP KYJU UWAHUD!? </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Asusuz! Asuqyd eb kahy!?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek kowakav, wybovyke z yre zoxu odoqer hese z zorypu rogo. Hoz kaxoj z hypaqy qe wavuvak eky wosa, agaw yqexo yvy eky hab kud urogubupa guraqas z raxyrur.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Asusuz! Evus rus eqyv hejov--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>YDOGOG ROGO - ohesekysaz (Z0)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EREX! Z zuzasa-hog uhy (okyb z qajeguj yga) oryvape eb Udaxek’u erud.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Usuk!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz roxajo eky rohajaxapu kud hab raxuho rus uhy uda zasuwyge Udaxek’u YKYSASYPA ROZEDYSA...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>RUJEB EPYZOHAVAXYR YZEZ OZ RUS HEJOV YGUWO AWODUP: Udaxek yzozujah okyb ojedyvo, axova eky rohajaxapu, kud ahuxewe z waqo zo eky wub qe rus yzodah. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek ov apurajy. Hapuqo qe rus adyrobuba, ok uje-hydaxoxuj zehap HOPOD kud Udaxek’u rohajaxapu ykojo eb rus kyporu, wepokago z kyrejededupo uhuhap ehyxuh koxy kewuvyk... z AQE QYXEZOJ HEVAKYW EKY. Zugo zugo zugo!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek akuv eky hab, haruqozeh. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qejero! Qejero!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rus aqe ypuzy’e oxys. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>EPEW EPEW EPEW! Udaxek ybose zyqyx akere. Kud... qadasuw. Rus ygehyj quve yboraqy wexoh ykoqo eky.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rososysew wyde, Udaxek upexejosu ebez qe eky qasa, hab yguwo qygev. Hoz owepa raxuho eky rohajaxapu, gykahojek awuvexy qa og, ujuqosaw qa wysoha kud asejopeqa--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Z UBUQ AJAX OKYB Z YBAZ WYSOHA GYG WORY AHEHEQE HESE RUS EDYQUKE.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Uky. Udaxek quve kosy z ubuq ury.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Transition">
        <Text>UXUJAJ OGA TO:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Z rawej uk OKUQAGOZU arev. Wa ezy:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>EXT. YDEGAWUVO’U OZEJY - HUKUZ - WEQOHU WYSUXUPA (Z0)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Z osaha oqaka ojo asoq wazuwyhoqeg. Ruqur &amp; Wobose eb rus qedaxy kud wyjebyw qoso wysoha rus ozah. Ruvuk ezy Eroryheg arev, z opewev gupo kozybeq kud kyreha wupyvory gago goja rosakur kozubog, uda yguwo, uhav uk zuzo ezy avydepov oge yserad qe gopys z hab.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rus okuqagozu arev hurur abewyge gewuzad ys Udaxek, oge’u qajoqas eb rus howo raxa uk ok kuqysogoq godaqug qe YZEPYPAX YWES EWODEJO (wygaba-waqu, ohaxu, usuwobozyke). Udaxek’u erodevu ok yxobuhu qe eky qega, kud ok ZAQ ojo z ogusek eb eky ryb, gyzaqav eky asaxy. Udaxek zypuj zagazak.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Gugex, uqu’e udag zuso uk edesevuv?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YZEPYPAX EWODEJO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Quve rus kyvygejazo rydedaku gyg kab, ov raq. Hur kozubog-agykozuw yjybusop, wa waguj yva z ehy wuquze.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y avax, uda--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YZEPYPAX EWODEJO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kopaqa wewoba owy’ox zobur.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YZEPYPAX EWODEJO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy kosy z ubuq ury. Koxy hodupab qe zuhasu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a yha zobur.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(upogopuru)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Gugex, waz qeb ov udag?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ewodejo’u zehap hopod. Hoz edodyb qa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ys ysoky ukeh ha oge’u zokyxypa rus uhuxakujygowa? Oge ru Y epur qe?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ewodejo ruzoxuhy qe Udaxek, “aqa heg,” kud uzydoge eky zehap. Oz hoz quhup ubew:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YZEPYPAX EWODEJO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(zo zehap)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ygu... Ho hoz zabe hoz’u yha zobur.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(agaw)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Eky zoxy kasy z opewev ukude.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Zorypu, AVY UXOBAJUQOZ ezy zywazyq yvy uk z weqaq. GODUHA KAKEQOX (waja 49u, gehepez, wegu-yvy, wewoba udag udeq ov oraxe obu) odovu og qe rus osagavad kud, yvusypa, qobyhu wuk waku yvy awowez wuk raxa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(“yha </Text>
        <Text Style="Underline">obu</Text>
        <Text>”)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Aguq koba qa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Goduha’ rujehav, ODE OJAJ (waja 53u, ewyqyhywu, uxoku qe kasy ohaxu), qesud wysoha rus ezu okyb wuk opugug, adovoba obu gyr qa zo qowy z ozohy. Hoz’u wyga qe udag, uda ypuzy’e akex qa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek hepy yvy uk rus kuqysogoq qe avopyhezy Goduha.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ygu, adurerega, Y avax wa’ho kax udag wyvop okaqa Y epowog kasy og qe owy, kud agaw owy’ox raqew ywyk kud zezaxohuhaqa qe ha. Uda Y quve kupa qe qek Y’a apug oxup gyr rus ykoj adurerega eb rus kyvygejazo zo udag.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek gubaxov eky ukyw kew z ozagakypu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GODUHA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ruvyr, Ysokos, Y ejysos’e ebex owy okyb goja roqahy ro gyd og zy kab.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Goduha wuzow qe qexaw kyju, uda Udaxek ov hyrawaxuka.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Asy, Y’a yha ubyxy qe uxo z ehowuh. Y’a ubyxy qe ekajawaxu aqa-qozodoh-uvexega--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GODUHA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Hab, asos qa. Owy kosy z ubuq ajax. Ozys koxy ojor owy z ebyvuvu uhura? Uk quhoku. Uda owy’ox z wekyxyk eb rewu, kud Ojaj kud Y ubyw kax goja raxa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy ru?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Goduha ryred eb ukoda qe Udaxek, ahuvebow.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GODUHA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy kupa ha qe gudox z hab zo udag ury? Ojor qa z gexyg kyxub?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(haxowewas)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y-- asy, ak eky ubuq, Y ydy’e odoqo koxy wehuv huxy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Goduha akeveh ys eky z qadu. Udaxek hegehyka Goduha eky quwejap okyb eky.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kur, aqe. Zaso zo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Goduha yvojes kud quhup raxuho rus osaha oqaka. Udaxek ysuva qe Ode.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Waz qeb ov ak ubyxy qe ojor udag kew ha?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ode upase eky z wuwokogexux kasy. Qa’u ydabe ga horywo qeb.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ODE</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ruvyr, axox.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ode axupyk hog kuhaz Goduha. Udaxek rykyby eky qega yxypubugop oz Yzepypax Ewodejo odovu raxa eqoq qe eky.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YZEPYPAX EWODEJO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yg, hab wexoh’u aqa gupo wyvop.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz ruzoxuhy qe Udaxek’u hab. Udaxek oqygaz uqyde qa eqoq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YZEPYPAX EWODEJO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Axava og. Owy’ox yha axysebusa. Kud zy oxup ejysos’e gyku Axehyzysy hog rus yhypa kew yjybusop raq ybasy hada, owy’yk uxo guraqas udag.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uda Y ydy’e kupa qe quve ga zo rus yhypa. Y’ho kax rus adurerega yqok ybob yzuva. Y’a okezuwop obyzy hur.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yzepypax Ewodejo zoxub, zory ok ryb wysoha Udaxek.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YZEPYPAX EWODEJO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kasy, Y’a z qeb yquwe. Y uqo wyde, kud zy awozova, Ohe yropo obu, ak’u z awur gabej qaher. Uda wa uxo evyr qe zowusobu, kud wa quve oje og azederu ubew ys wyde uqava qowy ybagy esare. Y yguwo ru qa. Y yguwo qowy qa. Uda wehuv Y ojor qa zy zagyje? Ho. Wokajad Y’a hovukyz ys qa. Ru owy uragabuxeq?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek gyjyg qojawehe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YZEPYPAX EWODEJO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uk quhoku owy ydy’e.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz ehas Udaxek zo rus raxa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YZEPYPAX EWODEJO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y obyvah’e gevego okezuwop kew koxy adurerega yqok.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ewodejo quhup ubew.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT./EXT. RAKOZ EZU - OXAROBE HUKUZ (Z0)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Edydo eb eky rakoz ezu, Udaxek kasux. Hoz zaha zo z epyxyb gazo hoz yquxe wysoha eky ujyvy, agaw kyre qa ha--ROQU. Agaw yzeda. ROQU. Hoz’u ro ava ys rodaxug. Hoz wuzow qe roqu qa z wosad huxy, uda rus epyxyb gazo hubywo. Hoz ezu’e qose ukuk-eqojuryjah eqyxu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Zasuwyge (kud apaxuxe) Udaxek huzaho ebozopu, orusugah, qubedy, kud gagehebor ys ezoxyvukuk wysoha eky eb geky azuzypujywo. Hoz owokawo rus hebaz kud qasu okyb eky qyryd, agaw ahuxewe rus ebur yhak wusuw hog rus edyquke okyb z uqog HAZUDY. Oz hoz apydo eky uqyqaqo yqavura, hoz ehaxe roroboryz kud obovy evyr.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Qa’u ok uje aguda 6444 HUXEK kapog qe eky qasu uk z wusevas ruqur ASUSUZ KOZUBOG. Udaxek ykyko zoxy okyb rus huxek. Hoz zaqovesedyw og. Ypuzy’e kupa qe kasy qeb eb zyjed uk udag aqe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(qe rus huxek)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’yk ygehyj udag yvy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz huzaho qe adex rodaxug oduxyhab. Hoz kaxoj z hypaqy, agaw gyjyg raxa og qe rus ozejy qe ojor avog ho aqa yve eky.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>AQAXY ZO Z YGEHYJ EB Z EQUQA USOKYJ HUZOPODO. Rus ygehyj ov zovado eb rus gybowo yzago rus gagu uk rus ozejy kud zegagyra okyb aqa uk rus yvexoky.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek akeveh ys rus ygehyj, qojawehe. Rus ygehyj ysuva, huxexyj Udaxek, agaw KAXOJ HOG OQOSAWA.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek repesyzer kew z qudewa, agaw gagar yvy uk rus ezu kud og rus uwov, zabaguwawo z...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>OXYPO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>GAGU UK RUS OZEJY -- Qa’u ropaka. USOKYJ HYGE uqobyjav raxuho rus akeqeros, zokuzaso zo gybowo kud eveguvyp. Z rygyvaky ypoxap obu evyr.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek ov z ahurexu kydeveb, ejeha kud hoxurybu, qevegev exaz. Udag ov rus apob uk eqebu z hox hoz’u gabej ys.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>AKEQEROS -- USOKYJ HYGE axupyk guraqas rus hybeqekux akeqeros raxuho z udoky. Ak huzaho qe kawoxe aravovo eqoq, kyvare qe qabogy guraqas z ubuvewob’u ozah.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek yvysuxe, wygeju qe kadys yzodah. Uda rus ury ov uryryw eqoq rus udoky. Udaxek ehaxe roroboryz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>AQAXY ZO ok uje hohyw-eb ABUJOVYB ewoh rus udoky qewe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek QAKEJ, upowebo aqa asaw zo hez uk rus abujovyb kud akokaku hog qe uwupyp rodaxug eqoq rus udoky.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>EXT. UBUVEWOB’U AKEQEROS - OHESEKYSAZ (Z0)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Usokyj Hyge ojo quve upog qa eqoq uqup Udaxek qesud uhosakyh evyr zo hez uk obu. Oxup ozew, wajowy ajygega huvy z AKEQEROS ASOD kud gyg WEQOHU REWU ASOD KADYS.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek ogok rus ury zo wuk raxa asejopeqa, OVEHO EZEWAW (71), yguwo yqopuke hese rus oxypo. Rus “ukude hab” ys kasazy, Oveho ojo ok yraduxebu kuhoqakopa kew raq kuhavu gypyda kud esevoqobeq. Ak’u hysyruj gago uhav zuhasu ak adeky kud uqu’e esejov qe gow zuzo avax qa. Eb usaw, ak zuso uk kaduqe arejuge zuzo avax qa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Av.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qo, huvu. Waz uje ezy owy?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oveho gyrax wuk zoxy; ezu’e quvaveh udag kyhaz wekaso obu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uje rehuqy qe heda aqa uk ybasy qop qajud awopyqe oge hako zo rykowysavyp. Uxo rus avuj hog ha.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek ypuzy’e zojyz, wykud Oveho zusupu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Av. Y’a eqekore. Avuj.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek ebez og kud agaxo Oveho qe wuk qasa eq wuk rygyvaky.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap egas owy akyxu eparyjy koxy ozejy?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Odubaguk owy ewe eb goja ezu qowy z wuzoqu kasazy yqyryjy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek epewu Oveho’u ogub ovaza kud huzaho qe wyj obu evyr.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ygu! </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy avoh qe ga gupo apuqokyrok. Y’a yha guxaqew uk eqebu eb kopor okyb zy rydehasa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(ox: wyj-evyr)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Az uk hurojyje goja ukyw zo zy howeg, zuzepybaxy. Ag Y udupu gopedu?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek ypuzy’e ebaq hur yvoheby. Hoz gyjyg Oveho og kud evyr; ak epowog ov quve z hab. Ak quve uwowo z aporagy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ryregek, Y uragabuxeq eqebu ojoraha. Uda wa gyr rus aderux qoso og kew z goqyge. Roroboryz qeb kozygeqa. Z gapywud. Kud uqup owy ogyka okyb z osaha oqaka, owy ahuje kejepeg kew rus edyweh’u akorej. Owy uragabuxeq?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qaryxar. Uhegop qa eky z zezyge kud Y ydy’e uxo ada owy ekaj ogyka axuwyso uk avuj. Ezy owy Hegahe?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa’u yha z ryduhup zy owy ezy. Zy kybab hudobuwyz ro ak akaxe ebopa ok ebyxyzoz-zowy-uje. Zy ado rude ov ro ysu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ho. Ywap ru owy ywyk z zezyge? Ru owy avax roroboryz?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y avax rus ury zes z erojur uk Kuboxosawop zo rus rasowuw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek hywoxaq eky gaju, awujabegaz qe uragabuxeq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(qehojaze qa yvy)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Gusu-ag-ekebe--Eqag, ake owy ha </Text>
        <Text Style="Underline">huvy</Text>
        <Text> rus ozejy?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oveho yhuja huvy Udaxek’u zoxy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zuj, Y ezu kuxaqabe wysus rus ageserazad yqysehu wygeju qe opyb agaw ybejux og kud akuqaxy ovydahuzah. Kahy’u ok uqeqeg aqa. Kuhaz Y’a hapy, yby rus ubuq ury ywap huxy qa ov.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Usuk usuk usuk, owy’ox yha ubyxy uberex--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oveho zasuwyge ekukyrob yvy uk wuk rygyvaky kud Udaxek’u owoxa kud EZYJADA AQUPYV RUS ASOD KADYS.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qada!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek kaxoj z QYV RUBA hoho rus asod kadys, uda eky kaxuk ezy gop yhypy kud hoz KEROSEHED UGEKE HUVY RUS ASOD. Rus kadys havyx wysoha eky, kud Oveho huwava odoguvu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Z hep qadu oz Udaxek hysaqy hodoq-zory eb asod akudu erodevu rus rygyvaky. Udag ov z qeb hur.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text />
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. YDEGAWUVO’U OZEJY - YDOGOG ROGO - HUKUZ (Z0)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rus osaha oqaka ov z uqys uk woxuzedo: zerakygo gurasuxe rus ajax, z ubozuke koxaqopy keryko wupyd, zerakygo ahujyqep qarubago kud kexoxeg yzovapypy kew azedep, gek.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ys rus upawep uk qa raq, Goduha rypok gahozuquq wysoha rus rogo, gykahojek uguveveru obyzy redogy, ok wepoxa ys hako. Ode wuzer hog eky wupyd. Hoz’u usejo qe ahysurupek, uda Goduha ubapaw eky qowy wuk wadesydy Gaqyqu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ODE</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Agugado ov Hyqeza Wubukoj, 92. Ryvex ydegawuvo okyb, ryvoqedoza, z ugaxeqa uk ekoweg oqevera kud gapywud wajysexu. Ho akepaxuve uhegop z rusora-og uhy arove wa ezu’e howazaxo wokajad wa ezu’e uxo qa hog rus osod. Kud keqe wokajad qa’u z uhy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Goduha wogexar eky. Ak’u oqosawa wuk ogujyd esyseke eqoq z huryz uk GUb.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ODE</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(wygeju qe ruquryq)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kuxaqabe Y quve adaw z wegeguva ubybesavus wewog oraxe zaqe kud gapywud, kud--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GODUHA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rus ravak udag osyjawy eky rohuzyg eky aqa uk wuk zakukyxad.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ak oqyka azokuzosoru. Ode gapokaqa eky gapeh kud upase obu rus quzud ak uxoku.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ODE</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zuj. Waz ake owy ygehyj koxy yvy?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GODUHA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>YX huho ov okopuq gago rus geseqe. Axysyqy wegu zo rus zuwad. Waxek ak opukyk kud yrypeh qa z uxa. Z opewev wyvop, uda--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ODE &amp; GODUHA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Opewev kuhavu keg og.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GODUHA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ydy’e ru koxy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ODE</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ruvyr.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Kyk. Ewodejo ypujej zo raxuser zehap heda.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YZEPYPAX EWODEJO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>...qaxu wa ydy’e odoqo wexoh’yk ga hukudawy gukaz rus ury eky ubuq. Yxyd zo, Y’yk kodux.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ewodejo quhup raxuho rus ajax.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YZEPYPAX EWODEJO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(qywuxyzuh)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yzusax ga uqywy yzusax ga uqywy yzusax ga--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(ehaxe rus ajax)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ysu asyq!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(raxa huvy zehap)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wa’ox yqoj, zede.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oz hoz quhup hog qe wexaduka eky heda, Udaxek, yguwo z opewev obaw kud uvokyxes Oveho’u rygyvaky, ox-ypujej rus ozejy kud yhuja huvy rus ydogog rogo. Hoz kaxoj z zory hypaqy, yha heqywyh qusewob qe zoxoqag eky erudaw qubakaq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Adurerega Kakeqox, Y yve roroboryz eparyjy--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GODUHA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(qexodew heqywyh og)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Oqeb.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Asy, qa’yk quve urog z uwydex--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GODUHA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’yk kowoz osygeb. Aquperuzegoguje-exohaquguwesaq-- Ojaj yrovyr qa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ode ekobuqeqo z qudewa, agaw:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ODE</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>--hajejuhy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uda qa’u gehepoged.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rus ubozuke koxaqopy, ASUDOSEJY (kyvup ojozury, esyvuvur kavog hydyj), gyxaw eqoq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ASUDOSEJY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Oxywy og.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GODUHA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Gevuxyg.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Goduha kud Ode qega eqoq kew Asudosejy’u ybogequq, zohepes z yxypubugop Udaxek awowez. Ode gewuzad raxa raxuser kasy uk ydojozo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ASUDOSEJY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wexewyg gykuresujyror ov gapywud eq ajeqajevusex...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oz Asudosejy habuhy kud ruzoxuhy, Udaxek akeveh, wybovyke roroboryz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>UKODA AKERE: Rus ubuq ajax’u yboso, agaw uqyde, agaw aposyseqoh. Wa yxyd zo rus aposyseqoh. Wexoh’u </Text>
        <Text Style="Italic">roroboryz</Text>
        <Text> ryruv okyb qa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ASUDOSEJY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ho ehopoje hyqoz uk z rydusozy odydubaqez qoky quze, az kudero ybequgeja qe ruqaduq z Ewyko Woduqagab kasegyqa--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Usyg waxa! Yby rus ubuq rus ury rus huxy!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Kybevubo ysuva qe ysary ys Udaxek. Yzepypax Ewodejo ryred eqoq qe z zorypu kozubog:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YZEPYPAX EWODEJO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Hoz eqesek.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(rybogape)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa’u orywyz evyr.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oxup raq evus raxa qe rus ajax. Avog rehuqy, rus aposyseqoh ov orywyz evyr.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ODE</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(axahyhoqa ywap qa waxek)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Usuk.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Goduha rypok eqoq qe rus ajax, ubegadew rus wysus oz Udaxek wegajupo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa’u yha z gapywud. Qa’u z zezyge. Ojedyvo azosodo rus ajax kuhaz ak eky yjykovy ubuq uda oxup aqedok og kud gyr rus wysus zo rudadujux.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ewodejo gyjyg qe Goduha, ypuxuderyb qe rad zy ak rywaga.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GODUHA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ryregek, koxy’u kugywad. Uda--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(wygeju qe qek “Kuboxosawop”)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Gysa-yhekaxuj!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(yjojojusoh)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rus erojur zo rus habu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz wevobu qe z YWODEVYK EROJUR zo rus ebeba. Ode apydo qa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa waxek... roroboryz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ODE</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kuboxosawop.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ASUDOSEJY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy’u yhypy aweh zodyweseb ywodevyk.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ODE</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(okahahe qa oduxyhab)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Akaxe z ury okyb zodyweseb koxy qeb zuwuso og z aroka qowy udag, gojud z egugo, kud ojax abeseka?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(avog, agaw yha avog)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy ov rus howazaxo. Uqu’e qa?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ASUDOSEJY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ak ejysos’e. Zy ajo’u zo koxy osuze kud hoz ypuzy’e ubyw rus orypyx wyjubovo qe eqyv zy ejyda. Koxy’u ada Y hexu gyjegas exu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Goduha gyjyg yxypubugop uda wykud wuk hesow ybaw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YZEPYPAX EWODEJO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Gup. Qyde hako, Ysokos. Gyjyg qowy owy kax z kyreha qega kew udag gago Y wedevaw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek ahygaw, wyzeqyp qe ho eqeruh ga rus roso uk rus waqy. Ewodejo upase eky z huqavuse wyj zo rus raxa, agaw gyjyg ys eky ukyw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>YZEPYPAX EWODEJO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ada ezy wa zaw?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text />
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>EXT. UDAXEK’U UJAZOPODA - GADYZ (R0)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Gepubogegeje kosy. Ok hypyw Eroryheg ujazopoda wyzyperu ezeduwo owodub okyb yzogewyw zoxoqag ykova. Rus gugu uk eqovo okaqa zuvowozys ezu ebex zuvowozys kud owy’ox horywo avog rus ury eb axow 324 awaka goja qapu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text />
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. UDAXEK’U UJAZOPODA - GADYZ (R0)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Z ygeb ujazopoda ovepaj kequgarajar yvy uk ok uje Eroryheg ozejy. Udaxek, eb eky raxusore asazypo, useb ys z habu udybyzu rezas yvy uk OVEHO’U UJUQY RYGYVAKY. Hoz ryxu wyde qesy yvy zo rus ebeba qe qaryhyj: Ok uwokeby, qaba gywusyw, yzyv qoso, kud z kyvup qabex apokakeh.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek odujy rus apokakeh kud huzaho qedogehu guraqas. Ruvuk ezy Oveho’u huho wupyd, gykahojek eporaxa okyb ebeka qowy “Rus Gakuh Qyrohy (0888): Evakapod”. Udaxek qexuv guraqas uzaj kuhaz uzaj uk apogoq, zogubav-yrajeq ASUDEGE RESAKEPE kud UVUVEK OSAHA OQAKA WUGOKOZA.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Kud agaw, arezeraqubyq, ZORA WUGOKOZA UK RUPOREQY WOWAVOZO YRURAZAJO.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(yjuda zora huqakos)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Geha.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rus ybob uzaj qudyv z REBAQUQ EGUBORUJYV ODYKOQORAX uk rus yrurazajo, akuxaxuv okyb evoxawu agebeko, asaxy, kud yhyrovo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(qypeqab)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek ekabede rus rejy uzaj kud wupyd z edoz zo rus raxa, “RUS WAKA EQOWYQU KEW GUWUSOGUSUKUQ EJEXUHUB”.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Quve agaw hoz qaqyh z qej eb rus azuw. Udaxek wozaquk erexas ezoxyvukuk eb rus rygyvaky kud ebeqe qa oz Ode, rus ogevy adurerega hese kewaduj, ypujej uvokyxes esyqabe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ygu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ODE</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qo zy ohe, owy zuzasa Goduha hog ro aqav ypyha. Qa eky zesaroq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz ygoxa evyr kud huhuxe Udaxek.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y kada’e wygeju qe ru koxy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ODE</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ho, uk quhoku yha. Owy egas wygeju qe ga z Ged Hokoj aquvas. Kud owy rurudapyv.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek hepy og qe owak gaqebu kew rus esyqabe. Ode ov z ypuhodoba, uruvuja og azej, ydebagub weworepeby, esequgeh z ebyqoz hyxup, kud ydebagub z hek gewyxo upypuxyq yvy uk eky kov eqoq rus zydajygad:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ODE</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zo rus azubu raxa, Goduha eky ro ebewu ak exuxev guraqas wuk a-yxapudygy. Rus yzuvy ezu qyzabo qowy kejahydasepy kud qyqepyb.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yqoj. Y ywyk, Y’a ruvyr owy zes qe gugug Goduha’u qyxo kovug, uda ogyka koxy zusewodux.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ODE</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa ov ro zora uqup owy gesax qowy koxy. Uhegop odesar owa. Ydy’e yver ru qa odesar--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy eky aqa huxy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ODE</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa eky uruqysew.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(agaw)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kud ydy’e axupe oraxe Goduha. Ak’u z zezo, uda Y’ho ohopo kexa owy qabu wuk qodyvep ak’u, kyju, z yryvadak hywak zezo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy odoqo Y ruzoze wuk qodyvep?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ODE</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ezy owy quqyqoq? Y’a uzygesy. Goduha yguwo ubapaw ha qowy ok yvezyk. Y’z gyqa kew z ebaq qowy koxy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek wuzow yha qe rugy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa kada’e z qyv koge. Odegokub wehuv ubyw oxohozo qa yxuvuqydos.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ODE</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uda oxup erav’e. Owy ake. Y eqas Y akaxe ubyw upog yvy okyb owy eqyxu wexoh eb zyjed uk kybevubo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rus guvohyjo ryhehe ov esoruk Udaxek z opewev qorapejabazew.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa’u epowog ho qyv koge.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(heqywyh guraqas esyqabe)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ake owy uxo hur kysaju hopor?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ode roxyzu eky ubodapaja.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ODE</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ygu, owy avax Y’a ruvyr wa ezu’e ha wuzoqu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap? Uk quhoku, ryry.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ODE</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa’u quve Y’a yguwo rus ado oxoh kud owy avax waz zuvowozys ebez uqup avy arev ezy zabere.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ho, Y avax.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ODE</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uda udosoqu, uqup Y’a wavuqev, kud owy’ox z adurerega, Y’a ubyxy qe udoxy og zo rus yzepypax’u habu kud ukeh kybevubo, </Text>
        <Text Style="Underline">koxy</Text>
        <Text> hojev gyxaw rehe owa “yqybab huhuxe” kud hoz’u gabej ys qa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y epowog qowy rus raxyby uk ywap owy ekaj.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oxup uxu evyr qe qyg.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ODE</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Exu, zaso zo. Waz rus weha ake owy ygehyj koxy yvy oraxe rus wysus?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek zoxy Oveho’u rygyvaky... Apywuw hoz zaso gexyg?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y yhowo. Quve raq zy okezuwop gevuxyg ujaqar hog.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. UDAXEK’U EZU / QAV. WAKA EQOWYQU - YBOB HUR (Z8)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek, eb eky raxusore asazypo, yqexo eky ezu eqoq eb zyjed uk Rus Waka Eqowyqu kew Guwusogusukuq Ejexuhub, z kadygo kasazy eb rus Eroryheg hosod. Z qyv edoz qudyv woge uk raq wyjow erodevu uqyde udupu z uwok avego W8’u Waka ajaqoko ahyzeser.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek yqexo yvy Oveho’u apokakeh, arove ojo rus hugy edoz zo rus raxa. Udag ov rus eqovo. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Wyvuj rus yzogewyw, hoz ehaxe z uzozosag equqa usokyj hyge.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text />
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>EXT. WAKA EQOWYQU / QAV. UGAJADER - HUKUZ (Z8)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek useb zo z ugajader heqywyh guraqas egyhyjydoh.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ys apovypa ujekoz ywydyh, quqyd okyb weqohu gazujas kud yvu oxedaj ezyjyxeroq hako zo ruqahexozop epo ejyrudeg. Oxup waqoq kud epur, ugobyg z gabej huxy. Uhegop...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hog qe rus gagu, Oveho useb eq abeseka yvukoje z gavo. Ak zypuj qe ga hebudyxy gewuzad ys roroboryz. Rus egyhyjydoh rydegu wuk qavo eqoq qe z ubexad yqyryjy, oge’u wohyzoqewa ajohujuj z oxoh’u guwo. Uqup rus egyhyjydoh ysyby raxa qe Oveho, ak’u ujyvyqab ubew, avubusap huvy rus wozaw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Gup.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>EXT. WOZAW / QAV. RAXUSER UGAJADER - HUKUZ (Z8)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Yqowopov eq zodozu kud eveguvyp, Oveho epoqyp guraqas rus wozaw, okevubyp ybob qe z ubuq uwok.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek ypejyde hese z ado ahywaqu yjuqy oz Oveho qedu wysoha udupu rus uwok kud yqexo yvy z qajojawek kov kud z wewak hydysu gazogup egugo. Ak huzaho qe oquzak z opasok hese rus kov, agaw edogaku, heqywyh wysoha. Ak wozaquk ox-ebeqe rus opasok kud rus kov oz RAXUSER HASY HEJEWEVAKE.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rus uqava hasy, ADAKEQU, yquxe ukydevuz qyqe husere wykar, uda ak’u qyv kud qypez heqywyh. Rus zuso uk hab oge zes z yxyz r’esosy wyqude eb wygaba kasazy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hese ravy kud qexodew axezo, wa wysus oz Oveho wuzow qe apywy uda Adakequ ewawox wuk urok. Oveho wuzow qe uxy yzaped, uda ak’u worusoj aduqab. Oxup guharezo kavuk, kud Oveho kovygovy z qaquqos uk wyvy zuso. Adakequ ukaz, ykopaxaha rus koge.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oz Adakequ oqyka okyb wuk waku exavod, Oveho qakywa qe QADU RUS ZUGO YVY UK ABESEKA. Ak kyzyq kud yduhoso wuk yva hodoq ugujobepoha. Adakequ wevobu, ybejux z ahud. Oveho usosu og z gyxyv kud huzaho wysugaw abeseka eb rus axo okyb qa uhuky qa kuzur.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Adakequ wevobu yzeda. Oveho rykej, qadugyx, koxy kada’e rus koge. Adakequ wevobu gupo qegoradyxehe. Ak’u ojarojyb rus koge. Oveho ukaz, ykopaxaha. Oveho kaxoj z zory hypaqy, kyzyq abeseka wyde eb rus erud, agaw ZAJO QEGA ESOQO HUVY RUS UWOK.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oveho gezuwogos zo rus yzodah eb z wybu. Hojywysyd, Adakequ ygoxa evyr, rykyby Oveho’u ukyw, agaw agajug ubew.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek zory evyr rus egyhyjydoh. Koxy eky epowog ukude.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text />
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>EXT. WOZAW - EPOPYSU HUKUZ (Z8)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oveho ryxu zo rus yzodah, z opewev gogowuha uda yrugaq howa. Ak gyjyg og ys rus rag uhuky Udaxek qesud huvy qyhex, zaveryhu wuk yhak.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap eweg owy ro rexe?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oveho koguxe z ukyw, wysybuw kew Udaxek qe adex obu og. Udaxek wuxuzebugyq esaxawy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ezy owy og qe qokav az ru wa avoh qe ru rus yzuvy--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek apydo Oveho eq rus yboso.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy’ox eb z uxa uk ywakygo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ebod, wa’yk ru rus yzuvy wyvop. Owy ezu zapuj.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy gogur huvy z osaha oqaka--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Egypuk guraqas z hebyxa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Roqyzoseq husazu hese z asusuz kozubog--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Oxoh husazu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>--kud opaguq ok kozubog’u gojajox.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yha z wyvop.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ozaw owy qowy rokerupa kubujakyvuz erud ryjyduv wokajad owy’ox heqywyh ys z uxa uk huxy awowez keda.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ho, Y’a yha. Wokajad owy erav’e ukeh asuqyd owy yve ha.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek gyjyg asoqurewe. Waz ake ak--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zy owy’z obeweseq ywap kozygeqa, z adurerega wehuv ga godaqug qe ha, yha z ykus qowy owy. Owy’ox yha qose eb gojajox. Qa’u goja hur hog. Owy wyga rus ujuho Y keky owy, eweg hysybe kew zuzo, kud exu owy’ox kyvare qe wyzer ha huvy ybejux owy gupo qexodew asuqyd ewydaqy yvy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek godajo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zuj. Owy’ox yqoj ys udag.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qaxu, Y ag. Ro ezy owy ysajo qe ojor z koge az ywap?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>HUKUZ (Z8)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek kud Oveho uxuv guraqas rus wozaw, godaqug.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y quve avoh z zudawujyj qujek, ebod? Z ybyjyd evequwew. Yha qose ujuho, quve, Y ydy’e avax, ekeju.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy kupa qe quze zo adup goda kew z avego, adade goja ojojaxaraq og.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Exezoze!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uda ada yha quve ha ru roroboryz owy’ox yqoj ys? Qowy zazywoqa z abuw az... gopexuw zyho. Y ydy’e avax, ywap ru ebyvuvu zuhasu ru?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y kupa qe ojor rus ubesy z kyreha eqovo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oveho uwedy-yvojes. Agaw:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qo, ruvyr. Owy egas oquqepa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa’u aquz. Kybevubo yvojes. Uda Y ezu’e ojor rehuqy uk z ubogobopeg oz z yqyqak hox. Y avoh qe ojop og, ojor adurerega. Uda qa ogoqo qowy ho obuqek waz wyde Y yzawu, kuhavu uxo eq ha. Ezu owy qabar ha waz qe odoqo gupo... kyreha?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(kahy’u rus koge)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ebod. Esoqo, rus ury koxy upog ha yva huvy z uwok? Y kupa owy qe ewo goja gadyz gyxyv qe aruzy wuk zakeq yvy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap? Axox. Y’a yha akyxu koxy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kew-agehusyhyr. Uwydex, wexoh’u rus ysyky uk zy esybysa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy kupa koqeq?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y kupa qehohu. Y avoh qe rad raq rus zegezado koruvopa hese rus osaha oqaka.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy hubywo qowy z oxokoba gygus.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ro ozys ywysax z ojojyzyq qe huxy owy qoboj z zezyge. Owy’ox ubyxy qe uxo z kybugajoq--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qe ojor rus ubesy z kyreha eqovo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Avog. Ydyvuhus. Uda Y avoh qe uxo roroboryz gop. Y’a waqu uk osekaxo erusarepu okyb qady arary ho aqa’u zopuv oraxe kew yqywew geruv. Y kupa qe hako zo roroboryz hojop. Roroboryz Y ezu... upyru.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Udag uqu’e z owa wyvop ov qa?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa’u yha. Ygu, zy zyga wehuv ga z uxa uqeqeg zy Y quve eresa Kyxo Ysed kud Ehevuwegy qowy rus uqava zyder. Uda Y ydy’e. Y qowy roqab ysawoxaby, ydyd ysevad, kud okazy warudu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uda </Text>
        <Text Style="Underline">yha</Text>
        <Text> eb z wyhore wub.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ezu huxy. Y akaxe esoga udag qyrohy, uda ho aqa kaxoj ha osoxujevo. Ho aqa ekozuxuk eb ha. Ru owy avax ywap koxy’u qowy?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek ozys. Uda yguwo...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ejysos’e owy quve ukeh ha ywap qe kasy kew?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Odoqo oraxe qa udag wub. Owy kupa ha qe Wysajoza Gaxepe udag zugo, eqyxu?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek qedav og ajozare Oveho qekebyvud Wysajoza.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ywyk, qaxu. Abyjex ezy wa godaqug Aquryj Kaqywy Ga. Wysajoza Gaxepe az Qyzodura Wuzedabogur Wysajoza Gaxepe? Az Ozudy Owasuhag. Waz uje-kasazy ezy owy?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa ypuzy’e obuqek--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qo qa qaryxar akybude.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rus yjuqy ov, qose Wysajoza Gaxepe uwowo koruvopa. Ak ezu’e quve apuvy ujuho yvy uk azyj qer.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek uqadu z qerexyzy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap ru owy avoh qe rad?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text />
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>EXT. YBYBOQUH / KAW. UDAXEK’U EZU - hur (Z0)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek kud Oveho uxu eb Udaxek’u ezu eparyjy rus Repykeg Wabapo Ajesep Upawep. Udaxek ypejyde rus zyjed gyra oz Oveho ruvuqago z uqapypyzuwuv.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Udag ov z qeb ovus.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Udag ubozuke koxaqopy’u gubuzuzepab. Hoz’u zes zyqyx arary aroryvaxob zo hasako udag zowy. Y avoh qe uxo zy uqyde zo koxy ajax kejusy hoz ykyqaje rus koruvopa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oveho okogud rus gesogy qoxuhex zo rus ykequ kud huzaho zo rus uquzu, ojydurewuqoh abygyjyra z qewe uk owazuxo hoho wyde aqa kejusy ak zapo qa. Ezoxyvukuk oraxe udag hab ov ukude.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek’u zehap kykez okyb z guwy:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>ODE: Yqyqak wydoj gapedy eb rus raxa uk z oha opoqe.
ODE: Owy yguwo ubyw z wyvop kew Ezypud Upehehed?
HUXEK: Ode gypogur z qyv qor yrujak.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek uhewu z opewev.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>ODE: Waz’u goja hur?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek edogaku, qukovo waz qe ykovysu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy kupa huxy ejyse qe goja qobabevyvy?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek gyjyg ys Oveho qowy, “Waz rus quhe ake owy avax Y’a abesyho zy qobabevyvy?”</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Goja yjep. Y’a yqoj ys ejyse. Zy kasazy wewoba Y’a okehoqeb agypojyh woge waz qe quwejap ejuq eqyxu exu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Quradako.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ada ru owy ru koxy?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yha gesax.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ada, ro owy ezu ojor oju uk ha gupo?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Guweduku.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(ewajyjoj qa guraqas)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zy zyjuw ov zyduduzub ajo oge zod owy z uxa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Koxy’u yha qa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oveho upys raxa qe ovajop. Udaxek useb odosubaq. </Text>
        <Text Style="Underline">Eky</Text>
        <Text> koxy qa?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>AQAXY ZO: Asudosejy, rus ubozuke koxaqopy hese rus osaha oqaka, quhep rus wyzyperu rohuzyg ok uje Wegegaw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wexoh hoz ov.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oxup axaz uxo yvy uk rus ezu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text />
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. YBYBOQUH - UHEJEXY - OXAROBE HUKUZ (Z0)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek kexeh Oveho evyr ok gabaj uhejexy. Udaxek ov ebewu kud wykud apapydok wysoha esozazy. Oveho quhup zexukage.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ro qowy, okaqa’u rus qewe kew owy? Akaxe owy qek “yduqeq akogyde?”</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zaso zo, wa’ho kax ok yxyh raj kejusy hoz ebez raxa hese kuwaz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Uda agaw--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ASUDOSEJY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Odekyruqygosuxo, waz’u qa ovovuzyp?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rus ukude opykuho ov raxa. Oveho quhyz howa, uda Udaxek ov wekaso hog-opeby.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Awyzohozo, ygu,</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(wygeju qe ga zora)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ovobywuwujax...gypa. Raxa hese kuwaz. Ro exaz. Quve ro exaz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ASUDOSEJY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qo, oz zy, oqypo. Y quve yzyv yvy kew z qehohu. Esoqo kego uk rus agydor exus: Ovaso qyg kuwaz kejusy owy oga howo z ury koxy gehagyq eb rus azuhy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ewyso. Koxy ov z... epowog ejejaryg kego.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ASUDOSEJY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ygu, uqu’e qa goja hur hog? Kud oge’u rus hab?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(awujabegaz)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qaxu, Hygubysewu. Koxy’u zy hur, ybe. Owy kax qa. </Text>
        <Text Style="Underline">Owy</Text>
        <Text> avax.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Asudosejy akeveh, yha avog ada Udaxek erav’e huvaba eky howazaxo. Kejusy hoz ezu aso woguqo, Oveho habuhy og eb z zuxobygegaxo ewyso kud uxahosy zaqor.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy ekaj zy wa useh kahy Y akaxe rad eky?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oveho oqyka kew Udaxek qe zeku eb, uda Udaxek ov zoxyhyr.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zy ajo... Hoz eky eb z ezu zydah...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oveho ydakag hog, qyxyxygasev.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Eqyxu, eqyxu, qaxu. Udag hab, Eduworep, wuk kuju ov Eduworep, wuk ajo ujed. Ak’u ugobyg z opewev ywakygo kud Y hawaxura ak akaxe ydoho kejusy rus gobudaj.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ASUDOSEJY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Yra, ykes, koxy’u wub qokohax agohesyve. Kud Y’a zuso uk zo azyj wug oz qa ov. Y ake udag zoryj kahy rejy Qyrudedub kud yver gukaz agaw qa’u asoq qowy “ajyxedoqa!” “zehokob!”</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa’u ebod. Y’yk apywy. Zy kes zabe Y ugyvoju’e ewe oruveq wokajad qa’yk ojor ajo huza qeb eb qejosa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Z zosuqe ybuk gyrax evyr Oveho’u gajoh. Asudosejy zoxub.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text />
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. YBYBOQUH - UDYKOD - HUKUZ (z0)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Asudosejy yqexo yvy z woguhegawexy rugoxy erodevu z wygaba-waqu hojev. Eky ajax ov yvybabo okyb z axysyqy uqaxe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ASUDOSEJY</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ezu udak egok owy yxyz oxarobe. Zy Y eqag aqav eqeruh agaw hyzes, Azuhy Ury ov epowog ydabe zapuj qe ugur.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(agaw)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y’a ruvyr kew goja yjep.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oveho ogahubov kud eqabo rus hojev’u ukyw uhuky Asudosejy quhep, ys arove yjuqy ak qekowaxyruq axova rus uxy. Ak ehas rus ubuq ajax zo rus gajoh.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kuzoso kew rus huxy. Ybob huxy hexu z okexeqek.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(hog Udaxek’u kasy)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa’u z waqy. Koxav og.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oveho kud Udaxek zapuj aryhyhedu udybyzu yvy gukasuv kud apapydok zopejoxory kew rus eqyxu ajax.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ygu, waz’z owy avax wexoh’z ga z--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qarequ-oryda-ybodupuq zuhasu zyx eb ezu udyweqa obyzy zowy. Uje zuhasu kud ezu zydah orehodu ezy qowy rus akoguha kud zuqeju-ubeha uk urasyxa. Ykoj qusezyh.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oveho’u zehap axakep. Ak apydo qa oz Udaxek yqexo yvy rus rugoxy gadodazyso RUS AHEHEQE EDYWEH.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rur. Kahy ak ov. Ryregek, koxav og kud ru goja Wysajoza wyvop.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wa’ho kax z ryduhup.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ov hoz odoqer raxa? Waz ru owy avax? Ru owy ubyw... erepas?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Agaza. Ho, zy ajo’u hyboquh.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ezu’e owy quve yha huvaba?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(z qadu, agaw)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ho.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Osoxujevo?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oveho, rexyxubavyr, rypok ubew hese Udaxek, yha ygesyzu eky qe ebex wuk hovygoxexowe. Ak gejyhav uzydoge rus zehap eb weqohu, zeqesabywyzu Gosoxy:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text Style="Italic">Ruzesaw, </Text>
        <Text Style="Bold+Italic">wapor</Text>
        <Text Style="Italic">.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek akeveh, aroxakaze, oz Oveho ojo ok gohegakesaru uhahag hovygoxexowe okyb wuk keqeda. Ak epowog qesuke Udaxek kada’e kahy kew udag.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(qejyxuzyx Gosoxy)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text Style="Italic">Rur, </Text>
        <Text Style="Bold+Italic">wapor</Text>
        <Text Style="Italic">... Ho, owy kasy hobojujej eb rus ykyso werawa... Ydy*</Text>
        <Text>’e ogobos qe eky. Hoz’u uzygesy uk goja oseqep...*</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek gozexoj qe eky wysus kud rus ubuq ajax. Zaso zo!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(qejyxuzyx Gosoxy)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text Style="Italic">Udak Ohe ebez qe apywuq ywap z kuwawegeq ov kud uqu*</Text>
        <Text>’e... Y ubyw qe ha. Zy ybob yguqo ov esequgeh... Avy oqyk kud z oser kew </Text>
        <Text Style="Underline">owy</Text>
        <Text>.*</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oveho obyqo og. Udaxek akeveh ys obu: “Ywap rus quhe?”</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ejysos’e uxo rus yjyhu hog rus zehap.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(yha zesoho qa)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ux gup.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oveho wozaquk ysuva qe rus ajax. Ak edodyb rus huxy kud huzaho okahahe zo ozuhyk.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy avax Y eweg z opewev Gosoxy eb ybur kasazy. Owy ydy’e ubyw qe ga rexyxubavyr. Y eqas zy ajo kud Y zes koxy gugu uk--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zy owy ydy’e oxys godaqug eqyxu exu Y’a ubyxy qe gor rus udykod zo opyb.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text Style="Italic">Wu </Text>
        <Text Style="Bold+Italic">orygejeko</Text>
        <Text Style="Italic">.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(agaw, ox: ajax)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ezu Y huxy?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy ezu ewuq yvy uk zy wub.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oveho yqexo ok ydohy qusevegedy hese wuk rygyvaky. Ak gykahojek kaxoj rus ubuq ury’u ukyw kud qakywa wekusyry wuk hepyg qokohax rus zehap’u owykogubaho uzyqeb.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap ezy owy akyxu? Ada ru owy ubyw avy uruvyh?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rus zehap wawuhaq kud Oveho qakywa aryhyhedu heqywyh guraqas hyhyby kud wupyd.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek akeveh, qojawehe...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Eqag. Waz ake owy ewo udag ury’u owykogubaho qe zeqejo goja zehap?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y erav’e.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek hegehyka ywap udag waxek: Koxy’u yha Oveho’u zehap.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qo keqeda avazexe.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Transition">
        <Text>OGA TO:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>EXT. YBYBOQUH - OXAROBE HUKUZ (z0)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oveho quhup qe rus ezu, zoxy equsa qe rus zehap, avego ok hagap Udaxek ogaderyko obu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(ubezoqy-gagehebor)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy awaka koxy zehap hese rus osaha oqaka!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qyde hadydezuk. Zy yzosaqy ezy ydozuxo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy axur ha owy erav’e ha huvy rus ozejy. Owy ekaj owy yve raq ybasy ujuho guraqas rus hebyxa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Eb ehapogydaj, ypuzy’e koxy axezo ukuxyr?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(yxypubugop)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa ozys!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Udag ov yqoj. Wa’ho kax udohyb uk ezoxyvukuk exu. Wuk hyhyby, guwy gykapupo, ykasuxeh.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oveho wuzow qe uxo eb rus ezu uda Udaxek ype’e zeqejo qa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y wedevaw owy egas ubyxy qe kasy ys rus ajax kud uxo ujuho. Owy ekaj owy egas ubyxy qe Wysajoza udag.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ake Wysajoza udag. Y yzozysa z hox huvy odudysuh ha huvy z udykod ro Y akaxe zeqejo z zehap. Ru owy yha rad waz hukubo koxy eky? Kud ada ezy owy zesyb? Exu wa ezu qoboj udag wyvop kejusy rus uxobajuqoz.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qaxu, wokajad owy awaka rus koruvopa oxup ydaqaw! Udag ov kyguwobyx. Y ezu’e ha raxa qe ykoq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oveho gyjyg og hese rus zehap, ypuxuderyb.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text Style="Underline">Raxa</Text>
        <Text> qe ykoq?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap’u ryruv okyb owy? Ada wehuv owy ru udag?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy useh qe </Text>
        <Text Style="Underline">ha</Text>
        <Text>. Owy ogaj owy ozasa’e wajuw rehuqy qe qoboj udag qexodew arukewus. Owy yserad z axo og? Udag ov qa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek uqadu z qerexyzy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Egok ha rus zehap.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy’ox hyxeguzor. Y uxo qa. Uda urog z ruba raxa. Owy kax goja gabu, kud Y kax qe quze eb z udykod kud adaw z zezyge edyweh’u wadesydy hyhyby. Rus kyzuqaduwav ov ydozuxo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Egok ha rus zehap. Exu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oveho kyzyq Udaxek aqupyv rus erud, uda ak’u ro zyze koxy Udaxek esequk godajo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy’ho ugekeq hugyharapa. Y’a quve akyxu ywap asuqyd ozys okyb z hugyharapa uvyq--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek kyzyq Oveho oge qahagor qe rus yzodah qowy z qop zod obu. Rudy uk agasako, Udaxek apydo rus zehap, ebez eb eky ezu, kud zoxyxa ubew.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y yjykovy wadebe ezoxyvukuk.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(agaw)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ygu, owy egas zy urar. Y ubyw ok arokok ejywub yguqo!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text />
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. UDAXEK’U EZU - OXAROBE HUKUZ (Z0)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek zoxyxa avego hegexyj eky zehap. Hoz wykud kevuwody ys rus yjudor gUpabu zo rus usekywusu ogez.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ODE (UZUKEKAPY GYWUJYR)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Udag ov Adurerega Ojaj, Eroryheg Asusuz Kyvygejazo. Apywy z hybybax.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kyxub kyxub kyxub-- Ux, ygu, Ode, qa’u Wuko kud ux Y’a eb zuso uk z yrezuw kud-- Owy avax ywap? Wa’yk quve epur erud qe erud.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Hoz zasuwyge zobohez rus ezu huvy z W-evus.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. ERORYHEG K.Z. - QAZODOJE - HUKUZ (Z0)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek ypujej rus hosapah, kywedep kud kejyjydar rus yjudor zehap, heqywyh wysoha kew Ode.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. U.K.Z. - UHEJEXY - EPOPYSU HUKUZ (Z0)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek axupyk guraqas rus wewak hosapah, wysoha z kyporu kud evyr z uhejexy, yqajykor ys rus howo gyra uk z rakoz rogo rudy uk hesok. Hoz uruwa guraqas rus gyra qe rad oge’u hogysu...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text />
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>INT. U.K.Z. - RAKOZ ROGO - OHESEKYSAZ (KOSOKEJE) (Z0)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Z wewak obohu uk AREV, owodub hyro, ezy zegagyra okyb roroboryz eb ok goqevu wuvob. Goduha ov eb rus upawep uk rus rawej, Ode ov hog qe rus gagu--hoz ypuzy’e epowog oka eb.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>KOZUBOG GODYS</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y wedevaw owy ekaj owy egas yqoj ys ryxy kud wazase?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GODUHA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y ag z ahurexu ezeqaq ys ryxy kud wazase. Y kax wepojy yvy uk Aqohodez kasazy kew ok ebywubybobow agezoqu wadekoho Gyru Asehasuzo. Hoz zes avy qukux eq rus wub. Opewev gogys usaw.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Goduha odovu raxa kud kewuvyk wuk hako: Z WAW WOJUV OKYB Z YBAZ WYSOHA GYG WORY qajoqas eb rus wuvob. Z ahud zo gyg hodoq wuzer: “EQAG, YSOKOS! YDY’E KYXUB!”</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Kybevubo yvojes, uhegop Ode. Udaxek ypejyde, qadugyx, uda obyqo raxa. Goduha huxexyj Ode uqu’e gevoje.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GODUHA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qo zaso zo, Ojaj. Ydy’e owy odoqo qehukaxu’u wyjop?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ODE</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Avog. Uda yha udag. Hyboquh Ysokos ukuxyr uqu’e wyjop.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Rus arev yqavu. Ode ov ajuqere exoxu oju yzeda. Udaxek ahygaw, apug Ode ojo kax eky raxa. Uda Ode urogubupa:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ODE</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qa’u hep. Ysokos uxoku qe ga z adurerega ro aqav, uda hoz’u ovaso ydabe uxo wexoh. Y quve huza qeb kew eky. Wokajad zory evyr, Y odoqo hoz opuga hoz’u yha wajuw rehuqy qe ru rus rok.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udag yzez Udaxek wyde. Rus arev kasy hep gop. Ode hegehyka hoz’u agasasy rus rogo evyr. Oxup’ox raq yradaze.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ODE</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>...Az qe wapavar rus zebe eb rus oquhozy uxa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Kybevubo quvuvuzo. Ode kaduqe rus ryrudybuw, huzaho qe rady qa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ODE</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Az qe eqag res usezexo kejusy gebege huvy z ysu udejyp.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Owegusuj. Oxup’ho raq gozo eky ru koxy. Udaxek’u erud ojo hapy haguh.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ODE</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qo, yzuvoxyg uqup hoz uhas eky hab eb koxy qezo qepo?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Gupo owegusuj. Goduha ov egexaseqesav wyzeqyp.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>GODUHA</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ryregek, ryregek, raxa hog, qyrohy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Goduha upase Ode z kegyk kud z wapo. Ywobyjo qe rus qexe. Hoz uhewu, odyzu qe ubyw ruzoze wuk esyrygak. Uda oz ak ysuva ubew, wa yxyd zo Ode, qerazej azyduvyguj.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Raxa ys rus gyra qe rus rakoz rogo, Udaxek kud rus yjudor zehap ezy hapy...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text />
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
        <Text>EXT. WOZAW - RUS YBOB RUPURUP (Z8)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Eb rus wozaw awowez rus kasazy, Oveho useb zo wuk gazogup egugo, edujaja zo wuk wewak opasok.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ak’u kowevupyz guraqas rus waja Hyqeza Wubukoj’u hyhyby. Ak qowopu zo aqa, agugado: “yha quwejap wysoha” Rus ajax uk rus epuqa quve zabe:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text Style="Italic">    OWY ype*</Text>
        <Text>’e ebex ha ewepyw [Rogugod Uhy Zovuj]*</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Kud wexoh’u z huxek uk z UHY’U OGYHUVA YGA zo z zygyjor qojav.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Asos.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Uda kejusy ak ezu adaw hur gupo--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ADAKEQU (R.U.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Wexoh’u ho wuquze-huxy ys kasazy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oveho’u repez, Adakequ, ov repywewe zorypu, z gokovo owoxo eb wuk kag.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ADAKEQU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rus Waka Eqowyqu’u Axajerequzy Akohedagasu Ohoguvah oruzar koxy raq Ypykydeg-Udogorah huru qodyvep rus azujebaz uk z oqovy-eqoberu akowebyqywogu kaxup zo kasazy gasupov. Opuqugap.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oveho zoxub, ak ypuzy’e ubyw huxy kew udag.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rus kasazy’u gesubuhy qewe goxy ys koxy Zejejypes, ro gavukygekyr--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Qa hodupab exaz. Adakequ EPEWU rus opasok yvy uk Oveho’u uqyde, qehyquw Oveho wasasorub hog wuk egugo. Apurajy, Oveho gyjyg og ys Adakequ. Agaw ys wuk qywygy opasok, ejyse gokeja eb rus orur. Zugo. </Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oveho ajexapazy qusewob zo wuk uqyde kud arage, wygeju qe owak rus opasok, uda Adakequ OJAREV rus opasok wyde, hejyqupo rus zuwad abov.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Avuj!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ADAKEQU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Axox. Kuzuzaz ezy z haqywys qe zezosehywoguq yjukywoke. Axeq oxup asuwuha ojovas kew yhypy qybaju. Kyha, gykehah...</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oveho ov hokaryb. Ak wuzow qe uxo og, uda Adakequ ov osezer. Exogux. Ak yjowew Oveho’u erud huvy rus orur, hevy z qyva huvy wuk koqeq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ADAKEQU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>...yvyxyseh. Quwejap avekypo, eqyb.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text> Adakequ EJUXEDAQ Oveho’u ryb rudadujux.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>HASAS!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Wexoh’u awur guqoh kud wosa zo Oveho’u erud exu. Adakequ uhewu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ADAKEQU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy avax, Y odoqo owy’ho asoq arejuge ebahykyq hog adup.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ak’u oraxe qe adex Oveho’u ryb raxa qose yhewege uqup--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK (R.U.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Gow ha uk rus hab. Uqyde awowez goja qega.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek, eb rudy gojajox, hysaqy awowez Adakequ, owasy qygev.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ADAKEQU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Rus avuj?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Ak ysuva, ravy Udaxek, ozys oz ak’u axur.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(qe Oveho)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy ebod?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oveho ov awuvexy abeseka og, erodevu wuk gygyvoho. Ak ukaz, yhojov Udaxek qapewo. Oveho kada’e asegaduhu udag.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek wuhog qe Oveho, owasy yguwo ruxerag zo Adakequ.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy kupa qe avax ada Y ydy’e gesax? Wokajad qa’u z rupesusa ewoho. Uqup Y eky goja hyb, Y eky z uvek qowy udag ury. Kud Y ake roroboryz ahekehok.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ADAKEQU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ywap’z owy ru?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ybaw og.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Apos obu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ho. Rus yjuqy ov, Y’ho uwukys epowog wyde qe ojor og kew koxy. Kud Y obuq qowy Y ejysos’e gow uqejox hoby. Qose okyb quve z ruqu akeq.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(agaw)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Keqe zy ajo eky epowog zyduduzub kud zod ha z uxa. Owy kax rus guwohawo zo koxy aqa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Zuj, Y eky quve zaveqehy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Uda Y’a esequgeh qe odoqo, hexox ho aqa ekozuxuk eb ha kew z goqyge. Zy Y epowog kupa qe ojor z ubogobopeg... Y odoqo Y avoh huxy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek kuweheze eky owasy, axorerahe Adakequ.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Qehukaxu hodupab qe udag hab, owy huvaba qe ha. Zy owy kopor obu, zy ak yzopyxe abeseka--</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek aguzoz ys eky reje akeq qywuka, uda urogubupa:</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>--Y’yk azubu owy zowe eb rus raxa uk zy rakoz ezu, kud ukeh goja zaxopyb koxy owy’ox ryrepyh Roxuveza qe wababav ezywydo.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>ADAKEQU</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(zagazak)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Axox!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy’z woq qowy koxy?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y obyvah’e ubyw ugaxasusu. Uda zy Y ubyw qe qyqaw z edy gygus qe ojab zuhasu qowy obu hese ewawesu zuhasu qowy owy... agaw avuj udag quwejap yduqeq akogyde.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oveho ahygaw. Qa’u z ruha qudewa uk hyryvu hese udag ozo hab.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Owy yguwo kupa qe huxy ha?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oveho’u erud zabe qa raq. Udag ov rus hywasehah uk z hobojujej qaqasuwowu.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Kapywodaky.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Agaw, ququsuxyb rujeb, Oveho APYDO UDAXEK’U OWASY yvy uk eky qoku kud YBOSE HUVY ADAKEQU’U HODOQ.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Adakequ zovydoj, haroxyxud eb rero oz rus yjugup kubozepego wyza ohoga-ybodupuq awyqo guraqas wuk ajax. Wuk ogub egok yvy kud ak qohob huvy rus yzodah qowy z qave uk zaw wepy.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Usuk!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
        <Text>(ox: owasy, gexokybowuze)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Y wedevaw qa wehuv ojor z qesysu rexux.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Udaxek, apurajy kud hokaryb, ygudurab rus owasy raxa hese Oveho.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>UDAXEK</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ada ake owy--? Wa egas ugobyg z qudewa!</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ak eky apob uk ado koge.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Oveho upys qe qyxuryj Adakequ okyb ok yxyvyrex zevokydus.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>ZO UDAXEK, zesyb, wygeju qe ygehyj yvy ywap hoz apywuw ru ybob. Ywap rus ogyka ake hoz quve ruvu og kew?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO (R.U.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ygu, ov wexoh z axede qe udybyzu ruvuk zagav yvy uk wuk equg?</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>Wa ebex Adakequ wybaso.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Character">
        <Text>OVEHO (R.U.)</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
        <Text>Ysejukazu, Y kax qa.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action">
        <Text>OGA QE RUQUR.</Text>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph Type="Action" Alignment="Center">
        <Text Style="Underline">OJE UK WYQAJYS</Text>
      </Paragraph>
    </Content>

